  <brief_title>Prevalence of Food Allergies to Proteins From Different Legumes</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prevalence of Food Allergies to Proteins From Different Legumes (Lupin, Peanut, Soy, and Pea) in Atopic and Healthy Subjects</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
